dct_description_sm: This collection of  Geospatial Data from the East View Global Census Archive presents Cuba's 2002 census in GIS-friendly formats including File Geodatabase, Shapefiles, documentation, and metadata. It is restricted to use by UWM Students, Faculty, and Staff for scholarly and academic uses.
